            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/14/shatintamagotchi/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=shatintamagotchi</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/14/shatintamagotchi/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 10:17:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1275178</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>沙田新城市廣場今日起舉行「YATA 驚喜盒子玩具展」，為期兩週至 11 月 26 日結束。本次展覽主打盲盒收藏與各類玩具，設置了多個展示區域，讓參觀者可以體驗各種新奇產品，並探索各類限量商品。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275236" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4848-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4848-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4848.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275237" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4849-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4849-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4849.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275238" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4850-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4850-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4850.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>會場限定商品與促銷活動</h2><p>本次展覽推出多款會場限定商品，如「Sanrio characters 搖籃不倒翁系列萌趣豆」、「Hangyodon 風味拉麵系列微盒 Pro」等。部分熱門商品如 Tamagotchi UNI 魔鬼版及 Sanrio characters 版亦於展場發售。現場部分商品享有折扣，例如購買《Sanrio characters》、食玩和《Rement》品牌的盲盒可享 85 折優惠。此外，購買《Tamagotchi》主機產品的顧客還可獲得 Tama Passport 一本，而購買指定數量產品還可獲贈吊飾。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275242" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4844-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4844-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4844.jpg 675